<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/_header') %>

    <main>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
        <p>Here are some common questions about our Local Community Portal.</p>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: What is the purpose of this portal?</h3>
            <p>A: This portal aims to connect local community members, share news, events, and resources within our neighborhood.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: How can I post an event?</h3>
            <p>A: Currently, event posting is managed by administrators. Please contact us via the Contact page if you have an event you'd like to share.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Q: Is there a cost to use the portal?</h3>
            <p>A: No, the Local Community Portal is completely free to use for all community members.</p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/_footer') %>
</body>
</html>